title: Junior 1 Bed- Prime Location! Hardwood/ Separated Bedroom/ WD
posting_body: ['Steps to fantastic Shopping, Dining, and Entertainment.', 'CTA and Metra Stops just outside your door.', 'Indoor access to the East Bank Club!', 'LUXURY AND STYLE', 'Walk in Closet', 'Elegant Granite Countertops', 'Stainless Steel', 'Panoramic Floor to Ceiling Windows', 'In Unit Washer and Dryer', 'Brand New Brazilian Cherry Wide Plank Flooring', 'COMFORT AND CONVENIENCE', 'Sundeck and River Walk', 'Outdoor Pool and Whirlpool', 'Complimentary Fitness Center', 'Party Room', 'Lush Dog Run', 'Garage Parking', '24 Hour Door Staff', 'Call or Email to schedule a tour!', 'We are available 7 days a week.', 'Downtown Apartment Company LLC', '730 N Wells Chicago, IL', '312-772-3929', 'REF# 5', 'Pictures are representative samples of the advertised unit.', 'In some cases, the actual units you tour may vary from the pictures based on the specific floor plan available.', 'Availability and prices are subject to change (and often do change daily).', 'Addresses, cross-streets or other geographic information, if provided, is intended to provide a general location of the advertised unit only; you should not rely on any address provided in this advertisement as an exact location of the unit.', 'Please contact us for exact addresses.', 'Units are leased unfurnished unless otherwise specified.', '12-month minimum lease term is standard for most units, but minimum term varies.', 'Equal housing opportunity.']
